    "body" : "<p><code>/usr/bin/java_home</code> tool returns 1 if java not installed.</p>\n\n<p>So you can check if java is installed by the next way:</p>\n\n<pre><code>/usr/libexec/java_home &amp;&gt; /dev/null &amp;&amp; echo \"installed\" || echo  \"not installed\"\n</code></pre>\n"
