    "body" : "<p>If you want to only check Java is already installed or not</p>\n<p>just type- <strong>java</strong> on the terminal</p>\n<p>and if you want to know about the version as well then</p>\n<p>type- <strong>java -version</strong> on the terminal</p>\n<p>Result will be look like:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/pG3vn.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/pG3vn.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
